        "body": "I often forget the location of the [media object page](https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.1/layout/media-object/). I don't know why it belongs to the layout category. From [the position of the `@import`](https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/blob/v4.1.3/scss/bootstrap.scss#L34) in the SCSS, it looks like it is treated like a component. How about moving the page into the components category?\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4065765/44942045-4c5b4a00-ade4-11e8-818e-0b994bea573c.png)\r\n",
