        "body": "I noticed that there are three issues about validation icon.\r\n\r\n**First issue:**\r\nThe icon hides behind scrollbar when a textarea has very long text.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4065765/44709163-e28d2880-aae3-11e8-86d4-9aa03766a906.png)\r\n\r\n**Second issue:**\r\n`<select class=\"form-control\">` show icon.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4065765/44709386-719a4080-aae4-11e8-848d-c6c37801a47c.png)\r\n\r\nIn [the docs](https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/pull/26824/files#diff-de50c25d3ce7f70d19229665020d03aaR772):\r\n\r\n> Background icons for `<select>`s are only available with `.custom-select`, and not `.form-control`.\r\n\r\nand @mdo [commented](https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/pull/26824): \r\n\r\n> Only applies to textual inputs and textareas with `.form-control` and selects with `.custom-select`\r\n\r\nbut icon is appeared. That is expected?\r\n\r\n**Third issue:**\r\n`<select class=\"custom-select\" multiple>` doesn't show icon.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4065765/44709632-10bf3800-aae5-11e8-9f8d-b0905fca9d7e.png)\r\n\r\n[All demo](https://codepen.io/anon/pen/LJZxgm)",
